== 評價 ==

這款遊戲普遍地獲得好評，在評論汇总網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的汇总得分为85分（滿分100分）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-4/nba-2k14 |title=NBA 2K14 reviews |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=2014-05-14 |archive-date=2015-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150831161047/http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-4/nba-2k14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[IGN|IGN]]編輯萊恩·麥克卡弗瑞（Ryan McCaffrey）給予這款遊戲9.3分的評分，並稱讚遊戲的玩法說道「擁有夠多的新特色，還有比以往更嚴謹的玩法，NBA 2K14超越了他的前幾代和競爭對手……再次地」。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=NBA 2K14 Review|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/09/26/nba-2k14-review|first=Ryan|last=McCaffrey|date=Sep 25, 2013|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate=Sep 30, 2013|quote=With just enough new features, and tighter-than-ever gameplay, NBA 2K14 tops its predecessors and competitors...again|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203153940/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/09/26/nba-2k14-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]的編輯湯姆·麥克西亞（Tom McShea）則給予8.0的評分，並讚揚遊戲很好，但是批評遊戲的設計。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/nba-2k14-review/1900-6414934/ |title=The King packs his bags for Cleveland |last=McShea |first=Tom |work=gamespot.com |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2013-10-01 |accessdate=2014-05-14 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120234616/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/nba-2k14-review/1900-6414934/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/nba-2k14-review/1900-6415551/ |title=Raise the banners. |last=McShea |first=Tom |work=gamespot.com |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2013-11-14 |accessdate=2014-05-14 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128011546/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/nba-2k14-review/1900-6415551/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[今日美國|今日美國]]的布雷特·莫利納（Brett Molina）在滿分4顆星中給予3.5星，並指出遊戲新的運球與投籃技巧使新手更容易上手，但是令老牌玩家們感到沮喪。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|title=Review: 'NBA 2K14' fit for a King|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2013/09/24/nba-2k14-review/2859787/|first=Brett|last=Molina|date=Sep 24, 2013|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|accessdate=Sep 30, 2013|archive-date=2013-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031073343/http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2013/09/24/nba-2k14-review/2859787/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 新增與變更 ==

除了前述的新配樂還有收錄歐洲聯賽球隊（移除了明星隊、美國國家隊、夢幻隊還有[[沙加緬度國王|沙加緬度國王]]2001－2002年的經典陣容），<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url= http://www.operationsports.com/news/664783/nba-2k14-video-player-ratings-classic-teams-and-euroleague//|title= NBA 2K14 Video - Player Ratings: Classic Teams and Euroleague|author= <!-- Staff writer(s); no by-line. -->|date= September 24, 2013|website= Operation Sports|publisher= |accessdate= October 20, 2013|archive-date= 2015-10-22|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151022174551/http://www.operationsports.com/news/664783/nba-2k14-video-player-ratings-classic-teams-and-euroleague/|dead-url= no}}</ref>還有一些自《2K13》後的全新改變：

* 「雷霸龍·詹姆士：邁向球季超群之路」模式，讓人聯想為《[[NBA_2K11|2K11]]》中的喬丹挑戰的縮減版，玩家可以控制[[雷霸龍·詹姆士|雷霸龍·詹姆士]]的職業生涯，以試著贏得更多的冠軍戒指（儘管選擇有限，還有他的未來仍為遊戲所計畫），不過這個模式並沒有在PlayStation 4與Xbox One平台上。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/review/a522212/nba-2k14-review-ps3-dominates-the-virtual-courts.html |title=NBA 2K14' review (PS3): Dominates the virtual courts |author=<!-- Staff writer(s); no by-line. --> |date=October 9, 2013 |website=Digital Spy |publisher= |accessdate=October 20, 2013 |archive-date=2015-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629152623/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/review/a522212/nba-2k14-review-ps3-dominates-the-virtual-courts.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 全新的招牌技巧，包括預購特典中的「LeBron Coast to Coast」技巧（快攻時的速度、敏捷度和控球能力提升4點，面對防守者時的投籃干擾影響將減少），另外還有「One Man Fastbreak」（快攻時速度、敏捷度和控球能力提升）、「Pick Dodger」（球員不容易被掩護阻擋）、「Tenacious Rebounder」（增加爭搶籃板能力）、「Flashy Passer」（減少“華麗傳球”時發生失誤的機率－見後方）、「Screen Outlet/Pick & Roll Maestro」（增加[[擋切戰術|擋切戰術]]執行力）。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.operationsports.com/news/656509/nba-2k14-new-signature-skills-revealed-including-pre-order-lebron-coast-to-coast/ |title=New Signature Skills Revealed |author=<!-- Staff writer(s); no by-line. --> |date=August 30, 2013 |website=Operation Sports |publisher= |accessdate=October 20, 2013 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304051728/http://www.operationsports.com/news/656509/nba-2k14-new-signature-skills-revealed-including-pre-order-lebron-coast-to-coast/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>“華麗傳球”為一種全新的傳球方式，按住左板機鍵並將右搖桿指向你要傳球的球員便能做出傳球動作（包含聲東擊西傳球）。
* 限制了「潛能值」和球員能力值的成長上限，並不會隨著球員進步而改變（在前幾代則會改變）。這看似是個微小的改變，但卻嚴格限制了王朝模式中球員的能力值成長。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://nba2kblog.wordpress.com/2013/10/20/nba2k14-player-potential/ |title=NBA2K14 and Player Potential: Why it is now so important! |author=<!-- Staff writer(s); no by-line. --> |date=October 20, 2013 |website=NBA 2K Blog |publisher= |accessdate=October 20, 2013 |archive-date=2015-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150819053548/https://nba2kblog.wordpress.com/2013/10/20/nba2k14-player-potential/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 由{{link-en|凱文·哈倫|Kevin Harlan}}、[[克拉克·凱洛格|克拉克·凱洛格]]和[[史蒂夫·科爾|史蒂夫·科爾]]播報超過50小時的全新實況報導，<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/nba-2k14-50-hours-fresh-commentary-every-year/|title=NBA 2K14 - 50+ New Hours of Fresh Commentary EVERY year|first=Andy|last=Hartup|date=August 25, 2013|website=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]|publisher=|accessdate=October 20, 2013|archive-date=2014-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140918014534/http://www.gamesradar.com/nba-2k14-50-hours-fresh-commentary-every-year/|dead-url=no}}</ref>全新的選秀會配音和「生涯模式」的全新旁白。
* 新的「訓練營」模式，指導玩家精進新的控制方式。
* 生涯模式中有自己的訓練選單，玩家不需要再回到主選單去做多個訓練課程。
* 在更新中加入了保持連線的[[DRM|DRM]]，要求玩家在遊玩生涯模式與經理模式時，必須保持連線至2K伺服器。不過這個更新補丁只適用於PS4與Xbox One遊戲版本，PS3、Xbox 360和PC版本則不受影響。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.gamefaqs.com/boards/691087-playstation-4/68068589|title=2K Patches in Always Online DRM to Next-Gen NBA2K14|date=December 11, 2013|website=[[Gamefaqs|Gamefaqs]]|publisher=|accessdate=December 11, 2013|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205355/http://www.gamefaqs.com/boards/691087-playstation-4/68068589|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此外，一些《2K13》中的錯誤在這次版本中也已經修復。也實現了預期的戰術路線與即時重播。

